now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=323896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D323896&d=cUe2kGK3L7mzwis%2B9D76sZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=ffb6ec5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D323896&h=f607dec4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=323896</a><br />\n<br />\n托馬斯亦畫有以民主黨總統為主題的《民主黨俱樂部》，當中有奧巴馬和克林頓。不知大家有沒有留意到，無論民主黨版還是共和黨版，都有一個共通點，就是有一個樣貌模糊的女性排眾而出，朝着一眾總統的方向走去。<br />\n<br />\n托馬斯在接受《時代》雜誌訪問時指，畫中的女性是未來的白宮主人，她無畏無懼地走入男性主導的世界。托馬斯指，藉此表達對女權主義的認同。<br />\n<br />\n侵侵捉蟲入屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11083ac32fb38d9eab55a3363eacdba426bfdf3","tid":864724,"uid":200328,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0baf8c043d08c236307b1f6baf20ac45bd53bfb0","tid":864724,"uid":2795,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84841eec6757dae24b35e67ea37f95f56c4ef111","tid":864724,"uid":158613,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"8c516fc0663d2bb489516173457ffc0969e97f1b","tid":864724,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:14:21.000Z","msg":"中間後面個女人先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個畫家話個女人走過去想加入<br />\n<br />\n代表女權主義崛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:41:28.000Z","msg":"死返入去洗碗啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:48:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=323896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D323896&d=cUe2kGK3L7mzwis%2B9D76sZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=ffb6ec5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A